      "text": "みなまで言わなくとも分かってますわ！",
      "startTime": 346.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-suz043.m4a",
      "text": "安心なさい。この仕事、トップアイドル成宮すずが\n完璧にこなしてご覧にいれますわ！",
      "startTime": 354.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
