      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-suz044.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり！！　完璧に理解しましたわ！！\n撮影では撮れ高たっぷりに盛り上げて差し上げますわ！",
      "startTime": 370.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "……なぁ、やっぱり少し休んだ方がいいんじゃないか？\n疲れていると判断力が鈍るって言うし",
      "startTime": 379.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-suz045.m4a",
      "text": "問題ありませんわ！\n大船に乗ったつもりで私に任せなさい！",
      "startTime": 385.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "（凄い自信だな……ここはすずを信じて任せてみるか）",
      "startTime": 389.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "（そうだ！　こんなに頑張っているすずを見れば）\n（お母さんも認めてくれるんじゃないか？）",
      "startTime": 399.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_03_02-suz046.m4a",
      "text": "さぁ、さぁさぁ！　次の現場へ参りますわよ！\nお仕事が私を待っているのですわ！",
